2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]   PRE-FLIGHT BRIEFING: V2 (ADVANCED INDIA VERSION)
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO] ================================================================================
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO] This version simulates a real-world Smart Grid (India RDSS standard):
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]   1. Time-Series: Processing a full day of data (96 slots of 15-minute intervals).
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]   2. Fault Tolerance: We inject random meter failures. The system automatically
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]      substitutes pre-generated 'dummy ciphertexts' so the network doesn't crash.
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]   3. Anomaly Detection: A rolling z-score monitor tracks the decrypted
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]      aggregates to detect power spikes or potential theft.
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]   4. Credit Scoring: The Gateway earns or loses reputation points based on
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]      the cryptographic verification of its aggregations.
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]   5. Billing: The system calculates estimated feeder-level revenue using
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO]      the official 3-slab DERC domestic tariff (Delhi).
2026-06-26 00:19:44 [INFO] ================================================================================
